Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.42,0:00:09.32,*Default,Mother,0000,0000,0000,,Kyo-chan is an older sister now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:11.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.43,0:00:16.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your older sister now. Do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.19,0:00:19.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She definitely hears you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:27.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time... the warm and loving Papa who still stood beside Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.74,0:00:30.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kyo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:32.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:34.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:38.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, I made a promise with Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A very important promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.64,0:00:44.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan! Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:46.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:51.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha, I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:54.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if the fever is gone yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:58.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.60,0:01:01.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The temperature's about the same as Asu, so I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.93,0:01:04.38,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going on my newspaper run.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.38,0:01:05.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:07.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.85,0:01:11.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan... there's no door there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.39,0:01:12.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.19,0:01:13.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.85,0:01:18.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you went on your newspaper run during rainy days, your cold got worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:22.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. In order to get well, I have to be energetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.59,0:01:25.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, you have to lie down first before you sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:39.97,*Default,Preopening,0000,0000,0000,,Mother went to heaven the year she gave birth to Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:43.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father left a huge debt after gambling and is now missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:47.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leaving only the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:50.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place we live in is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.24,0:01:52.59,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a beaten up 40 year old apartment with one room and no bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.91,0:01:54.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.26,0:01:57.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, when spring comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.99,0:03:34.15,*Default,Title,0000,0000,0000,,A Day of Colds, Promises and Mother
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.08,0:03:54.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, the congee's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:55.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.68,0:03:57.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:03.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still hot, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:07.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.39,0:04:14.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your appetite's still fine. It looks like you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.96,0:04:25.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not eating, Asu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:27.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:29.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't feel like eating right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.62,0:04:31.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:36.96,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you sweat, your body has to be scrubbed clean so I can change your clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.96,0:04:37.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:48.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How does it feel? Need more ice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:50.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine now, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:55.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just rest up while I take your temperature periodically and you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:02.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps a cold once in a while is pretty nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.65,0:05:08.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. I have to get well soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:12.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't have Asu worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.45,0:05:22.93,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I have completely recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:25.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you had me worried there. That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:27.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to my sister's care.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I'll work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:34.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My cold is finally cured!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.03,0:05:38.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Asu, I have to work harder to gain back the sick days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:45.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? She's not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back! Asu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.43,0:05:51.81,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? The faucet's not turned off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:53.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:55.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asu?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:05:59.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asu! Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:11.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:16.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owner-san! Asu... she needs to go the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.88,0:06:18.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:20.66,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Asu? Are you still cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:25.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get her to the hospital like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.43,0:06:25.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:29.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. We'll have to call for an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:30.24,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.55,0:06:42.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come I didn't notice at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.70,0:06:45.86,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asu was sick already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:49.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet... she still took care of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:58.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:02.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyo-chan, Mama is all right. It's only an ordinary cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:03.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:09.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the only thing Mother said when she got on the ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:11.73,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After she got sick, she never came back from the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.11,0:07:30.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll have to stay in the hospital for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:32.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand. I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:33.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is troublesome...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.14,0:07:38.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the rest to us, but if the sister stays here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.40,0:07:41.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, but can you let the sister stay with her for tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:52.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... Asu... I'm really sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:57.51,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to become stronger... stronger than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:01.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to become someone who Asu won't worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.36,0:08:03.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:07.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kyo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:08.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.94,0:08:10.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.87,0:08:18.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please protect this child.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I will protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:25.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will definitely protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:28.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:33.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time... I already promised that I'll protect Asu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:37.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.34,0:08:48.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:53.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:56.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry that I worried you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:01.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too... I didn't notice your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.34,0:09:03.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:07.42,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, let me take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.26,0:09:11.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's made it through. You don't have to worry too much anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:12.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:17.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of checkups afterwards, so leave the rest to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:18.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.63,0:09:19.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:20.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.38,0:09:27.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:32.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:13.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I wonder if Asu wants to eat some apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:20.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.92,0:10:28.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.57,0:10:32.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Asu isn't here... I can't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:37.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I protect Asu like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.18,0:10:39.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.79,0:10:59.95,*Default,Eyecatch,0000,0000,0000,,(Being hungry is the best flavoring in the world.)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:08.40,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(Time, turn back! The foods have passed their expiration date!)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.54,0:11:22.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Onee-chan, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:23.98,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Asu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:25.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:28.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can get up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:29.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel a lot better than yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.61,0:11:30.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:32.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:35.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I peeled some apples.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:36.25,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan peeled them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.89,0:11:39.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:43.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, you didn't soak them in salt water first, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.50,0:11:45.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.13,0:11:49.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:52.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:54.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:58.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I really can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:03.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:06.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Owner-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:08.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:10.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.46,0:12:12.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:15.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Leave it up to me. You go to school now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.87,0:12:17.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:26.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.46,0:12:30.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:41.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyo-chan, please protect this child.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:44.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:46.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will definitely protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:03.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted Asu-chan to regain her energy, so I brought my guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:05.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you want to sing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.64,0:13:09.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... that's what I had planned... can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.72,0:13:12.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a hospital. You'll get scolded at.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:14.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:18.37,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I really wanted to hear Ichinokura-san sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:21.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel much better when I hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.83,0:13:26.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, since Asu-chan says so, I'll sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:35.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan is late...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:03.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dandelions...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.79,0:14:17.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are Mama's favorite flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.17,0:14:31.28,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring some to Mama in the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:35.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time Mama sees dandelions she always smiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.13,0:14:39.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, if I bring her some, Mama will definitely get her energy back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.33,0:14:47.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time... I came here to pick flowers every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.48,0:14:54.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama! Mama! I picked some flowers again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:12.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:16.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also... couldn't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:17.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.71,0:15:24.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyo, you picked some dandelions for your mother again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.27,0:15:26.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.73,0:15:29.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really can't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.31,0:15:32.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already promised, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:39.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing Kyo-chan's dandelions lets me forget about my sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.22,0:15:45.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:50.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother's smile...she seems so happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:52.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.78,0:15:57.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why does Mama always smiles when she sees dandelions?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.26,0:16:00.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because the dandelions look so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.89,0:16:02.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.07,0:16:02.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:05.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the dandelions are like Kyo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.16,0:16:07.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:08.30,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:13.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dandelions... look a lot like the smiling Kyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:16.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why every time I see dandelions, I will smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.79,0:16:18.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.60,0:16:25.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Mother wasn't smiling because of the dandelions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.12,0:16:29.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was smiling because she saw me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:33.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was smiling because she saw my smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:35.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:40.79,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always looking after me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:43.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.91,0:16:58.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet I was always giving Asu a pained look...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:00.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Asu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:02.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.70,0:17:06.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan is someone irreplaceable.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:07.56,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:14.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan is Onee-chan. Please keep it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:19.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I understand. Onee-chan is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:21.99,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:27.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what was I doing... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asu!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.78,0:17:41.16,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I completely forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.26,0:17:46.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that only I can do for Asu, the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:48.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.19,0:17:57.48,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan... she's fine, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.57,0:18:01.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not tired out because of me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.64,0:18:06.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Living in the hospital requires a lot of money... I hope she doesn't stress out...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:17.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:24.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:33.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}(Asu, good night. Please get well soon!!)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:35.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.08,0:18:42.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:44.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.11,0:18:46.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:56.62,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan's smile is just like a dandelion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.19,0:19:02.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on your discharge, Asu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:04.22,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.35,0:19:05.94,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you take care of yourself afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:06.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:08.13,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.01,0:19:15.49,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Onee-chan. I want to go somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.77,0:19:26.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you have a cold, don't force yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.46,0:19:27.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:30.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the beginning Onee-chan's cold was much more serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:35.01,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so worried that I forgot to take care of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:36.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Asu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.74,0:19:40.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:40.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:43.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.52,0:19:48.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right here, I... Mother asked me to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:48.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:53.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, I heard it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.99,0:19:57.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your older sister now. Do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.22,0:20:00.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:03.27,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with... Mother's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.18,0:20:07.85,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ask you, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.07,0:20:10.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.83,0:20:14.58,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please protect... Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:19.53,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Asu, you and Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.53,0:20:22.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I don't remember her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:24.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think I've heard this many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.09,0:20:27.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I've promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.47,0:20:30.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:32.61,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.64,0:20:43.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother, it's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:47.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can keep this promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:54.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A beaten up 40 year old apartment with one room and no bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:57.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.50,0:21:00.90,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, when spring comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.84,0:21:06.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:08.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they've bloomed!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.00,0:21:17.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're really fortunate right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.01,0:21:21.77,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan, oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.02,0:21:24.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole room is covered with cherry blossoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:03.75,Default,Opening,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Omoitei modorenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.07,0:02:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we can't return to our memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kyou wo ikii asuotsukamo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.00,0:02:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's seize today and search for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hitorimo ochimo hitorikiri janai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.44,0:02:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may be by myself, but I'm not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Futarimo ochimo futarikimi janai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's only the two of us, we're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Soredemokoboreru namida no mae ni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when seeing my tears about to fall,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Egao nashi ugokyuu dekiru noka nai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can I still smile and take a deep breath?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:03:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Omoitei modorenai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:03:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we can't return to our memories
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kyou wo ikii asuotsukamo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.44,0:03:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's seize today and search for tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kagega eno naikimi no owoseki wa kokoro ni aru
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:14.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That unreachable jewel is there within your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mukai kaze ni shingokyuu
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.71,0:03:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Face the oncoming wind and take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:50.27,Default,Ending,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ta ainaiosha be iga
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when everyday talk
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.82,0:21:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Fuinito gi re ta tokimo
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.82,0:21:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,gets interrupted,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ko oshite sobani iru dakede
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all I need is you by my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Anshin tekiru
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I feel safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.27,0:22:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Obekowo ruwa ni na de ru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.27,0:22:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind face of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Soyokaze ni tai ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is just like a gentle wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.90,0:22:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Gyuto gyuto te to te wo tsunaitara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.90,0:22:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We tightly hold each other's hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.34,0:22:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sakamichi wo kage a ga ra wo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.34,0:22:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and run up that hilly path together.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ashita wa zettai tanoshiine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow will definitely be another happy day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.39,0:22:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nara n de yuko o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.39,0:22:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us walk shoulder to shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Gyuto gyuto kaze wo tsu kama e tara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tightly hold on to that flowing wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Ryuote hirogeto doketai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.33,0:22:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to spread my arms out and give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.90,0:22:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Gyuto gyuto ashita no asa atemo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.90,0:22:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We tightly hold each other's hands tomorrow and the day after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Nara n de yuko iisho ni yuko o
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoulder to shoulder, let us walk ahead together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.33,0:21:25.33,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,

